<div class="title">Lime Green Slurpee</div>
<div class="substance">Cacti - T. pachanoi</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Bombaysapphire&Exact=1">Bombaysapphire</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Bombaysapphire. "Lime Green Slurpee: An Experience with Cacti - T. pachanoi (exp11767)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Nov 3, 2004. erowid.org/exp/11767</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
